    "description": "<p>This dataset contains pediatric EEG data recorded during an SSVEP-based BCI experiment that implemented an SSVEP stimulus personalization pipeline. Data from 47 neurotypical participants aged 5-18 years is included in this repository. This data is made publicly available with the aim of promoting the development of signal processing methods specific to pediatric SSVEP-based BCI data.</p>",
